question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Animal dander (substance)?
answers:

             FROM procedures p 
             JOIN encounters e ON p.encounter = e.id 
             JOIN patients pa ON e.patient = pa.id 
             WHERE pa.first='John' AND pa.last='Doe' 
             GROUP BY p.description 
             ORDER BY count DESC 
             LIMIT 1;

            [Q]: 'What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Animal dander (substance) and a specific insurance provider?'

             FROM procedures p 
             JOIN encounters e ON p.encounter = e.id 
             JOIN patients pa ON e.patient = pa.id 
             JOIN payers p2 ON e.payer = p2.id 
             WHERE pa.first='John' AND pa.last='Doe' AND p2.name='Blue Cross' 
             GROUP BY p.description 
             ORDER BY count DESC 
             LIMIT 1;
